* File sharing Application
  This application is based on Node js , Express as framework and database Mongodb
  File can be image or video  
    - 'image/jpg','image/jpeg','image/png','video/mp4'
  Used Multer package for uploading
  File stored used in cloud
    - cloudinary

* Githup repository


* Starting application
  npm install //inside root directory
  start server 
    - npm run server
    - default port 5000
    - http://localhost:5000
  start Mongodb
    - mongod

*Api
  - tested through Postman

  *. signup
    - http://localhost:5000/user/signup
    - Post
    - body params
      - email and password

  *. signin
    - http://localhost:5000/user/signin
    - Post
    - body params
      - email and password

  *. File Upload
    - http://localhost:5000/user/upload?title=xyz&description=xyz
    - Post
    - body
       - Form-data
          - image
    - params
      - title
      - description
    - Headers
      - key 
        - authorization 
      -value
        - token
  
  *. Edit File
    - http://localhost:5000/user/file/:fileId?title=xyz&description=xyz
    - Put
    - body
      - Form-data
        - image
    - params
      - title
      - description
    - Headers
      - key 
        - authorization 
      -value
        - token

  *. Get Files of a user
    - http://localhost:5000/user/files
    - GET
    - Headers
      - key 
        - authorization 
      - value
        - token

  *. Delete File
    - http://localhost:5000/user/file/:fileId
    - DELETE
    - Headers
      - key 
        - authorization 
      - value
        - token
  
  *. short url
    - http://localhost:5000/user/file/shorturl/:fileId
    - Post
    - - Headers
      - key 
        - authorization 
      - value
        - token

mongod --config /usr/local/etc/mongod.conf
mongod --config /usr/local/etc/mongod.conf --auth